name: Rare Punkleton
description: Nobody likes watching someone let themselves go, but this is a regrettable inevitability for the Rare Punkleton. Lacking the hardiness of the Common's Smunkin-like head, it is doomed to decompose faster and turn into a sloppy mess. Donning a paper bag to limit the embarrassment, it's lucky that this ghoulish Rare Seasonal is only really active during a time of dress-up - it fits right in, and no one's the wiser!
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 1 day 7 hr 45 min, Enhanced Time: 23 hr 48 min 45 secd
